    <div id="main"> 
     <p> <img src="/resources/images/rec_center_main.jpg" alt="." width="484" height="180"> </p> 
     <h3>Health, Fitness and Adventure at the Student Center</h3> 
     <p>The UCR Student Recreation Center is the hub of recreational, intramural and club sports on campus. Whether it is working out in our extensive gymnasium, playing pick-up basketball, taking a class or going on an adventure with our Outdoor Excursions program, the 80,000 square foot facility is the place for fun and fitness at UCR.</p> 
     <p>The facilities are <strong>free to all UCR students with current ID</strong>. Others may purchase quarterly memberships or day passes for admission</p> 
     <p>Programs offered through the SRC include:</p> 
     <ul> 
      <li><a href="http://recreation.ucr.edu/competitiveSports/Pages/IntramuralSports.aspx">Intramurals</a></li> 
      <li><a href="http://excursions.ucr.edu/">Outdoor Excursions</a></li> 
      <li><a href="http://recreation.ucr.edu/competitiveSports/Pages/RecreationClubs.aspx">Recreation classes and programs</a></li> 
      <li><a href="http://recreation.ucr.edu/competitiveSports/Pages/Team%20Sports.aspx">Club sports and recreation clubs</a></li> 
      <li><a href="http://recreation.ucr.edu/fitness_wellness/Pages/landing.aspx">Health and fitness, including personal training</a></li> 
     </ul> 
     <h3>Hours of Operation</h3> 
     <table class="data2" border="0"> 
      <thead> 
       <tr>
        <th>Days</th>
        <th>Student Recreation Center Hours</th>
       </tr> 
      </thead> 
      <tbody class="striped"> 
       <tr> 
        <td>Monday–Thursday</td> 
        <td>6 a.m.–midnight</td> 
       </tr> 
       <tr> 
